<br>
Anyone have suggestions as to what would be the best 'reasonably-priced' weapon combo for a low 40s warrior moving up quickly (i.e need to be good combo up til 50 or at least to high 40s)? I'm not looking for 'big, pretty hits' but rather solid DPS and ability to hold aggro. Procs and crits are icing so I've got crusty and dex sucks (it's about 65 as currently configured - also like to hear thoughts on whether others think that dex is a second order effect - pretty much negligible when it comes to real work in my view).<br>
<br>
I don't have a 60+ main to buy me weapons - have to buy with loot sales, thus the reasonably-priced stipulation - no way I can afford a SBoZ or other 40k type item. Max is about 2k per weapon, maybe 3 (for reference, Centi LS goes for about 2k on my server, JBoM 1k, Lammy 1.5k, Wurmy 1k, Defiance 3k, Lucy 10k, SBoZ 40k).<br>
<br>
I currently have a Wurmy, JBoM and Centi LS. Centi is always off hand, and I switch between then Wurmy and the JBoM for primary. <br>
<br>
